This paper discusses the scalability issues and bottlenecks related to current blockchains in supporting Electronic Health Records (EHRs) for hospital systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
